column5: Tried a search with no luck....looking for anyone who fishes Scout Lake Resort, on Lac Seul. Would appreciate any info--email fine if you prefer.
Try www.fishlacseul.com , that should get you to their website. Never been to the resort but fished Lac Seul for 6 summers now. It's a good one!
I have not been there in a couple of years Always had I good time and always caught pleaty of fish If you have any ? you can e-mail me jeffster
snwhited----sent you a return email-but it was returned---said your account is full.....PLS email me again.. THX
